      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;the-traveller-and-the-axe&#34;&gt;The Traveller and the Axe&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There was once a traveller who found himself lost in the woods as night began to fall. He knew he would not last the night without a fire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a clearing he found an old axe, its blade dull from years of neglect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“I must chop wood for the fire,” he thought. “But first, I must prepare the axe.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And so, he set to work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
